beer.beer_description: Simple Coercion was brewed with high protein grains to give a full body without excessive sweetness. Simcoe hops are added throughout the brewing process contributing tropical fruit, citrus and woody aromas. It was also fermented with two expressive yeast strains that produce fruity esters and promote hop biotransformation.
